title: Advocate - Burning Daylight
description: "In 2002 a group of friends from Colorado started a company called Advocate skateboards. For three years we traveled all over the U.S. as well as to Brazil and Spain making friends, building skateparks, and skating & filming along the way. In 2005 as it became apparent Advocate was on the decline, we decided to release we collected as a way to remember the fun we had during the 3 years of Advocate skateboards (2002-2005)."
